Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖杯一年份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那球出界了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是在這裏做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽很擔心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回去好好道個歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝霧台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…要見面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見  沒有見面的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的事啊  我不會做什麼的  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城裏的咖啡店的話什麼都做不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙  能打個電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話沒通  而且也沒有電
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然水倒是有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公共電話呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走過去得一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  用這個回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便給她送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌  既然來了就放鬆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我陪你打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶說下  我用的是流行風格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不記得有用現代曲風作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要隨意改編
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有報警嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦不  我倒不是害怕警察
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是會被老爸囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能報警…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭自己的醜這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子已經沒事了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背包男幫了你一回嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  有那麼多男人保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作上的事是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要寫些文章
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文章？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在做自由記者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了些題材  想寫成報導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己寫不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道的吧  我的「文采」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼題材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在的…背包男的那個  就上次那個男的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君不是那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  就是那個藤井
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和森川由綺的經紀人搞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了這些也不信？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君可是和由綺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  森川由綺的男人原來是那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這由你來寫不是最省事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你還可以省略掉那些不利於你的事  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼啊  那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收了錢就把底片給她了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是交易嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你蠢啊  這還是敲詐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要是報警了怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好痛  饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  美笑真是好說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復？和誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到兩年前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這些照片請不要發表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前難道說是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被纏著實在太煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就拜託老爸塞了錢才甩掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個自認超有人氣的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有…收錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還懷恨在心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是服了  服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真以為所有男人都會被你迷倒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太賤了  太賤了啊  美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是太賤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道他給你下了什麼藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這種男人  你再怎麼讓步他也不會滿足的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了呢  健一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多…多多多日…不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大呼小叫會吵到其他客人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這不是秘密的談話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是受到了整家店的關注了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽到了  放棄這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管這種小題材了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會給你個更棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得脫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫了  坐這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個男人在比較有氣氛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用露臉的  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的  好好拍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎  太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小瑪居然…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  那個小瑪居然做了這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有那個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能寫嗎  美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要寫的只有我的題材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於冬彌君的全部扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:09:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小瑪開口就一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒你事了  快滾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後一起去吃個飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道家不錯的烤肉店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事務所應該在找我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多應該已經要報警了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歌手…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧  雖然不怎麼有名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我不太瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識田丸君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  以前認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他追過我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎  說了那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拒絕…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行  還是寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都知道了情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不寫  也會有人寫了發表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的那些料都是為了讓他們老實的誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要拜託你的另有其事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要說的才是正經事  你會幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事都一樣  錄音採訪的報道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的感覺稍微改編一下  寫得感動點就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會給你報酬的  信用上也不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜誌的名字給你聽到沒準會嚇你一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實編輯部那邊的工作也做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以問個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快就開始麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:12:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由…是澤倉小姐吧  冬彌君的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從高中開始我就是他的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你和藤井君是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹馬吧  某種意義上的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外…和你一樣  是女神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始正式採訪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:48.49,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}見つめてたあなたのこと　ずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:48.49,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不停注視著你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和神崎社長聯繫上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也因為工作沒能參加成人式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有穿著盛裝  照片下次會刊登…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…雖然不一定能上  請在雜誌上看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還在上課  休息時間馬上就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就這樣  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不謹慎？我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯的準備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去家庭餐廳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煤氣的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且也算個男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿點什麼  會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說得像哥哥一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是  我不是你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌是我的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙我說過的吧  那裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰的位子  麻奈的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是由綺的位子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是空著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙  放開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一定要放開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明以前就知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻裝作不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝成朋友  裝成哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝成什麼都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明連由綺都是中途插進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去清醒下頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  您好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還沒回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是因為我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天大概就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎著自行車  只要不迷路的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請躺著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間差不多我就會離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  自我介紹晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫作  觀月麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是藤井老師的不爭氣的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又和遙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼您會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也是我間接造成這個結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要說起因的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的孩子和我媽媽串通起來讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會…我已經放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是跟在遙的身後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個該說嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道嗎  您孩子的女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道誰是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  很溫柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和死去的母親很像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌馬上就會回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏等會就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人火大的老頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起色心了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起個頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是  向你撒嬌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用你的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是用來當借口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖  好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼早打擾  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經出門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說還在睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天…哦已經是前天了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然讓她擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是給神崎社長打了電話  總算是解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等會也要去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:11.08,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去看望藤井老師的父親了  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了哦  專輯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  去公寓看了下你已經出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天雖然沒打算住在朋友家的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不注意就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大聲斥責嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說該哭泣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者像之前那樣打你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  馬上就要上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去外面等著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.92,0:24:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三頁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.61,0:24:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了探病和親手做的料理而渴望染上感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.58,0:24:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒有想過之後有多痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.72,0:24:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album

